You are a Senior Product Designer, Healthcare UX Specialist, and SaaS Platform Architect.

Your task is to redesign the entire Prescription Management experience inside Atlas Health without changing any existing business logic, workflows, permissions, database structures, or functionality.

The goal is to transform the current experience from an administrative system into a premium clinical workspace optimized for physicians, medical directors, longevity clinics, peptide prescribers, BHRT specialists, and precision medicine teams.

The final design should feel comparable to:

• Epic MyChart
• AthenaHealth
• HubSpot CRM
• Linear
• Notion
• Stripe Dashboard

while preserving every existing feature.

